Commentary: Zulfiqar Babar to Roy, no run, looped up and Babar finds turn with the new ball. No shot offered
Zulfiqar Babar to Roy, FOUR, dropped short and outside off, Roy rocks back and thumps it away to the midwicket boundary
Zulfiqar Babar to Roy, 1 run, sliding into the pads, nudged to leg for one
Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, no run, skids on outside off, and beats the attempted cut
Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, FOUR
Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, FOUR, tossed outside off, Zaman comes down the track and drills it over the bowler's head
Anwar Ali to Roy, no run
Anwar Ali to Roy, no run
Anwar Ali to Roy, no run, just short of a good length and outside off, drags a pull behind square on the leg side
Anwar Ali to Roy, 1 run, good length and outside off, Roy leans back and creams the ball to point
Anwar Ali to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, pitched up and angling away outside off, Zaman presses forward and jabs the ball to mid-off
Anwar Ali to Roy, FOUR, bail-high short ball on off, Roy sits back and dispatches it to the midwicket boundary with a pull. The boundary ruins the over
Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, no run, uses his feet and pokes the ball to point
Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run
Zulfiqar Babar to Roy, 2 leg byes, tossed up and angling down the leg side, Roy skips out, and does not meet the pitch. The ball grazes the pad and rolls away fine on the leg side
Zulfiqar Babar to Roy, FOUR, Roy pre-meditates, goes for a reverse-sweep and nails the ball from the stumps. Sends it over point
Zulfiqar Babar to Roy, FOUR, Roy hits the repeat button now. Tossed outside leg, Roy fetches it from there and reverses-swats it over point again
Zulfiqar Babar to Roy, 1 run, very full on the stumps, non-turning ball, push-driven to mid-on
Anwar Ali to Roy, 1 run, Roy jumps down the track, takes a half-volley, and belts it down the ground
Anwar Ali to Fakhar Zaman, no run, full-toss outside off, driven straight to extra cover
Anwar Ali to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run
Anwar Ali to Roy, 1 run, yorker on leg stump, dug back to the bowler
Anwar Ali to Roy, SIX, half-volley on middle, free-hit, Roy does not need any second invitations. He launches it over the long-on boundary. Monster hit
Anwar Ali to Roy, SIX, length ball on middle stump, Roy clears his front leg again and blasts the ball over midwicket now. Back-to-back sixes. Lahore off to a flying start in Sharjah
Perera to Fakhar Zaman, FOUR, slower full ball outside off, Zaman leans into the drive and laces the ball in the gap between covers and mid-off
Perera to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, another slower cutter outside off, dabbed towards point with soft hands
Perera to Roy, SIX, 112ks slower ball on off stump, Roy picks it and hoists it over the straight boundary. Thisara can't stop the bleeding
Perera to Roy, 1 run, short of a length on middle and leg, flapped to midwicket
Perera to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, back of a length on off stump, shovelled away with the bottom hand to wide long-on
Perera to Roy, 1 run, back of the hand slower ball on middle and leg, tapped towards midwicket
Mohammad Nawaz to Roy, no run, short ball, darted in at leg stump, pulled to mid-on
Mohammad Nawaz to Roy, FOUR, dragged short on middle and leg, he goes over the top. Pulled over mid-on
Mohammad Nawaz to Roy, no run, Roy backs away outside the leg stump, Nawaz follows him. Punched down to long-on
Mohammad Nawaz to Roy, FOUR, fractionally short on off, Roy slugs it with all his might over midwicket
Mohammad Nawaz to Roy, 1 run, Fifty off 24 balls for Roy. Shovel-pulled away to deep midwicket. Stop him if you can
Mohammad Nawaz to Fakhar Zaman, FOUR, Zaman skips down the track, meets the pitch, and belts it straight past the bowler
Hasan Khan to Roy, 1 run, dropped short on off stump, pulled powerfully to wide long-on
Hasan Khan to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, down the track and works a length ball into the vacant spaces on the leg side
Hasan Khan to Roy, no run, flighted on the leg stump or just outside, reverse-slapped straight to point

Hasan Khan to Roy, OUT, Hasan produces the breakthrough for Quetta. Sir Viv is pleased in the dug out. Slides in with the arm as opposed to turning away. Full delivery, Roy eyes up the leg side but misses the big swipe. Hasan hits the off stump and celebrates
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, no run, pushed through on middle, defended
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, no run
Mahmudullah to Fakhar Zaman, FOUR, Zaman gallops down the track and drills a very full ball to long-on
Mahmudullah to Fakhar Zaman, no run, slides on outside off, leans back and chops to backward point
Mahmudullah to Fakhar Zaman, FOUR, Zaman uses his feet again, Mahmudullah drags his length back outside off. Smeared over extra-cover
Mahmudullah to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, picked off the pads through backward square leg
Mahmudullah to Umar Akmal, 1 run, slower offbreak, dabbed with the turn to midwicket
Mahmudullah to Fakhar Zaman, 2 runs, dropped short and outside off, leans back and cuts square through the off side
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, 1 run, tossed up outside off, driven on the front foot to long-off
Hasan Khan to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, flatter and just a shade outside off, Zaman drops to one knee and drags a slog-sweep to deep midwicket
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, 2 runs, full and angled in on off, clipped away to deep midwicket running to is left
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, SIX, Umar comes down the track, takes it on the half-volley, and pumps it over the covers
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, no run, Umar uses his feet again, the bowler shortens his length. Punched to cover
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, 1 run, full, straight ball, knocked down to long-on
Zulfiqar Babar to Umar Akmal, 1 run, good length ball on middle and leg, Umar hangs back and clips through midwicket
Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, no run, Zaman uses his feet and nearly chips a return catch
Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, no run
Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, Zaman skips out, this is a full-toss on the leg stump, he opens the face and drives to long-off
Zulfiqar Babar to Umar Akmal, 1 run, more round-arm than normal, angled in full, whipped away to cow corner

Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, no run, 98ks dart, Babar hurled it flatter, seeing Zaman step out. Sarfraz does not collect the ball cleanly. He swipes the bails on the second attempt, but by then Zaman is safe
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, FOUR, tossed up on off, Umar rushes down the track and dumps Hasan over his head. The runs continue to flow
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, no run, uses his feet, Hasan pulls his length back. Umar checks his drive and chips in front of cover

Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, no run, fractionally short and outside off, chopped to backward point. Mix-up between the wickets, Zaman is nearly halfway down the pitch. Umar isn't interested. Zaman has enough time to hustle back
Hasan Khan to Umar Akmal, OUT, Umar comes down the track again, this time he is cramped for room. He attempts a wild swing and only miscues it to Mahmudullah at long-on
Hasan Khan to Mohammad Rizwan, no run, full and drifts in, blocked back to the bowler
Wicket: ['Umar Akmal c Mahmudullah b Hasan Khan 17 (14b 1x4 1x6) SR: 121.42']

Commentary: Hasan Khan to Mohammad Rizwan, no run, full, grips in the surface, and spins away outside off, forward-defensive to cover
Perera to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, full and wide outside off, Zaman, having come down the track early, reaches out and ends up scything the ball over point
Perera to Mohammad Rizwan, no run, back of a length and outside off, sliced away to point
Perera to Mohammad Rizwan, no run, back of a length and outside off, cuts and can't beat Shehzad at point again
Perera to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, much fuller and outside off, Rizwan allows the ball to come to him, then opens the face and runs it down to third man
Perera to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, back of a length and outside off, flashed on the back foot to extra cover
Perera to Mohammad Rizwan, 2 runs, good length and outside off, dragged away with the bottom hand to wide long-on
Hasan Khan to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, comes down the track and hammers a full ball to long-off
Hasan Khan to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, uses his feet and clips it away to wide long-on
Hasan Khan to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, fired on the pads, whipped to long-on
Hasan Khan to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run
Hasan Khan to Fakhar Zaman, SIX, shortish and outside off, unleashes a clubbing swing and sends the ball soaring over wide long-on
Hasan Khan to Fakhar Zaman, 1 run, uses his feet yorks himself and jabs to cover

Zulfiqar Babar to Fakhar Zaman, OUT, tossed up and outside off, Zaman hares down the track, but is nowhere close to the pitch. Hoicks at the ball and picks out Shehzad at deep midwicket. No fifty for Zaman
Zulfiqar Babar to Delport, no run, really full on off, driven back to Babar
Zulfiqar Babar to Delport, 1 run, fired into the pads, clipped to midwicket
Wicket: ['Fakhar Zaman c Ahmed Shehzad b Zulfiqar Babar 47 (31b 6x4 1x6) SR: 151.61']

Commentary: Zulfiqar Babar to Mohammad Rizwan, no run, full on off, stabbed back to the bowler
Zulfiqar Babar to Mohammad Rizwan, no run, much loopier and outside off, gently pushed back to the bowler
Zulfiqar Babar to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, backs away outside leg, opens up the off side and drives inside-out to long-off
Mohammad Nawaz to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, flatter on off, chopped from there to short third man
Mohammad Nawaz to Delport, 1 run, back of a length on leg stump, forced away to deep midwicket
Mohammad Nawaz to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, Rizwan skips out, the bowler holds this full ball back. Check-pushed to long-off
Mohammad Nawaz to Delport, 1 run, yorker on middle, jammed down to long-off
Mohammad Nawaz to Mohammad Rizwan, SIX, Rizwan finally makes good connection. He charges down the track, gets a half-volley on off stump, and lofts it over the bowler's head for a six
Mohammad Nawaz to Mohammad Rizwan, no run, slides on with the arm on off, Rizwan hangs back and plays it back to the bowler
Mahmudullah to Delport, 1 run, good length and angled in on middle from around the stumps, hangs back and clips through midwicket

Mahmudullah to Mohammad Rizwan, 2 runs, tossed up just a shade outside off, Rizwan skies a slog sweep in the air. Deep square leg runs across, Hasan I think, attempts the catch, but loses his balance and tumbles over the boundary. He, however, had the presence of mind to tip the ball into the playing field before going over. Deep midwicket tore to his right. Nearly a relay catch
Mahmudullah to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, down the track and slogged in the direction of deep midwicket
Mahmudullah to Delport, no run, back of a length and outside off, flashed away to extra cover
Mahmudullah to Delport, 1 run, faster on off stump, punched away to wide long-off
Mahmudullah to Mohammad Rizwan, SIX, slower through the air on off stump, Rizwan drops to one knee and smites a slog-sweep. Puts Mahmudullah into the stands beyond midwicket
Mohammad Nawaz to Delport, FOUR, drifting down the leg side, picked up and swept over short fine leg
Mohammad Nawaz to Delport, SIX, length and outside off, smeared over midwicket for another six
Mohammad Nawaz to Delport, 2 runs, short and outside off, pulled away on the back foot. Deep midwicket dives to his right to stop the ball, parrying it to wide long-on
Mohammad Nawaz to Delport, 1 run, shortish on leg stump, swiped to deep midwicket
Mohammad Nawaz to Mohammad Rizwan, SIX, Bisects deep midwicket and long-on. Rizwan comes down the track, and slams a short ball away. Hits the ad cushions on the flush. It's a six
Mohammad Nawaz to Mohammad Rizwan, 2 runs, very full on middle and leg, whipped through midwicket
Perera to Delport, no run
Perera to Delport, 1 run, leg-stump yorker, which is squeezed away to long-on
Perera to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, full on leg stump from around the wicket, Rizwan paddles it down to fine leg
Perera to Delport, SIX, Perera errs in line and length. Full and sliding down the leg side, Delport picks it up and whips into the stands beyond square leg
Perera to Delport, 1 run, low full-toss on the stumps, shovelled to long-on
Perera to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run
Anwar Ali to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, length ball on off stump, slogged away to deep midwicket
Anwar Ali to Delport, SIX, full-toss on off, Delport backs away, lines it up and dispatches it over the bowler's head. 200 on for Lahore
Anwar Ali to Delport, 1 run, Delport backs away outside leg, this is probably a slower ball. Under-edged beside the stumps on the off side
Anwar Ali to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, Rizwan aims to slog-sweep over midwicket, ends up skewing the ball to point
Anwar Ali to Delport, 1 run, length ball on middle and leg stumps, hacked to deep midwicket
Anwar Ali to Mohammad Rizwan, FOUR, short ball on off stump, chest-high delivery. Cramps Rizwan for room. But he still swats it away to the square-leg boundary
Perera to Delport, no run, full and wide outside off, Delport backs away, swishes and misses
Perera to Delport, 1 leg bye, yorker just outside leg, grazes the pad and rolls fine
Perera to Mohammad Rizwan, no run
Perera to Mohammad Rizwan, SIX, comes down the track, meets a full-toss, and bashes it over the top, clearing a leaping deep midwicket
Perera to Mohammad Rizwan, 1 run, full on off, plonks his front leg forward and swipes to deep midwicket
Perera to Delport, 1 run, low full-toss outside off, forced to long-off. Lahore finish with 200
